abstract: Karrie Webb's golf career has come full circle, opening 2015 LPGA season at Golden Ocala Golf and Equestrian Club, site of her first victory in United States in 1995; Webb has earned more than $19 million on the Tour over her 20-year career.
lead_paragraph: Webb opened the 2015 L.P.G.A. season at the Golden Ocala Golf and Equestrian Club last week, the site of her first victory in the United States in 1995.

headline.main: After Many Milestones, Karrie Webb Returns to Where It All Began
